CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 15 reads: "3. Operator Terry Price of the Angel Pink Creme Press puts the finishing touches on a completed hair-do of one of the fair visitors in her attractive booth"
